The header of the popup will be changed to the step 3 name "בחר חלופות"

Clicking on one of the alternative food names will mark the alternative with "V" icon.

The alternative that was chosen will be added to the menu page.
The user can choose no more then ? alternatives.
On step 3, the "Confirm" button will be enabled, clicking on it will close the popup and move the user back to the menu page (updated with the food and alternatives that the user chose).

fields.description:
This page will be the last page in the session flow

As a user I will be able to see the "was this a special event?" page and answer it
1. this part is optional, user can end the flow session without filling it 
2. beneath the question will be a free-text box, limited to 40 characters 
2.1. The free text box will say "type here..."
2.2. once the user clicked on the text-box the writing "type here" will disappear, and a native keyboard will appear
2.3. user will be able to close the keyboard by tapping anywhere on the screen (beside the text-box)
2.4. if the user didn't type anything and closed the keyboard \- the "type here..." writing will appear again
3. once the user typed an answer it will appear in the text box. tapping on anywhere on the screen (beside the textbox) will close the keyboard but the text he filled in will remain
4. by tapping on the "Done" button, the session will end as described in the header description.

fields.description:
As a user I will be able to see the "Where are you?" page and answer it (this page will come after "how present do you feel) 

Yaron \- Ignore the small question mark on the print screen, its not updated. 
1. The user will see the following question on the top of the page: "Where are you?"
2. The user will be able to see the following answers \- 
2.1. Home
2.2. Work
2.3. Other
2.4. Location
3. Each answer will have its own logo
4. the user can pick one of the four answers by tapping on it
5. Once the user chose an answer it will be marked
5.1. Tapping on a different answer will remove the mark from the first answer and will move it to the other answer
6. By tapping on the "location" answer the system will use Google Places in order to locate nearest places in a 5 meter radius \- a pop-up with the location will appear

6.1 by tapping the "close" button user will be able to close the pop-up

6.2 by tapping a location, the user will go to the next question on the flow
7.  The system will ask for the user approval of using his location
7.1. If the user didn't give his approval for the use of his location the location answer will be disabled

fields.description:
As a user I will be able to see the "whom are you with" page and answer it (this page will come after the "where are you" page)
Yaron \- Ignor the small question mark on the print screen, its not updated. 
1. The User will see the following question on the top of the page: "Whom are you with?"
2. The user will be able to see the following answers \- 
2.1. Alone
2.2. Partner
2.3. Family
2.4. Children
2.5. Friends
2.6. Other
3.  The user can pick one of the six answers by tapping on it
3.1. If the user chose the option "other" a free text pop-up will open and the user will be able to type his answer
3.1.1. by tapping the "OK" button the answer will be saved and the pop-up will disappear
3.1.2. by tapping on the "cancel" button user will be able to close the pop-up, his answer will be deleted
4. Once the user chose an answer it will be marked
4.1. Tapping on a different answer will remove the mark from the first answer and will move it to the other answer

fields.description:
As a user I will be able to see two tabs on my profile page \- המתכונים שלי, מתכונים מהערוצים שלי

# next to each tab will be an indication of the number of posts appearing under it
# desktop \- the tab will include two post in a row, and 6 in a cloumn (until pagintation)
# at the bottom of the page will appear a "לעוד מתכונים" button which will load more recipes. this button will appear only when the user has more recipes to load

המתכונים שלי

# tab will include recipes the user marked as favorites (meaning all the recipes appearing under this tab will be marked as saved in favorites)
# user will be able to delete a recipe from this list by tapping on the "saved to favorite" button \- button will change to "add to favorite" and the next the user will load this page it will disappear from the page
# above the feed will be a headline \- "ספר המתכונים שלי"

מתכונים מהערוצים שלי

# this tab will be called in the mobile version "מתכונים מהערוצים"
# above the feed will be a headline \- "מתכונים מהערוצים שלי"
# under this tab will appear all the recipes that appear under channels/creators that the user is following (=added them to his favorite, appearing under the "my channels" section on profile page)

הפוסטים

Will be very similar to the feed in the creator page \- 

# user will be able to see a photo of the recipe and an indication of the length of the recipe video. 
# user will see the creators photo, the creator's name, the number of views for recipe (total number of entrance to page), the date the recipe was uploaded, a short description, a favorite button (add to favorite or saved to favorites)
# The number of views will be controlled from admin \- admin will be able to hide that criterion from users
# By tapping the "favorite" button \- will be an indication (a full/empty heart), the button will change to add/saved to favorite \- and the recipe will be added or deleted from favorites in accordance
# by tapping a specific recipe \- user will go to the recipe page of the specific recipe

fields.description:
As a user I will be able to see the 'chef team' and will be able to sort them manually

1.The chef team will sort according to the way the admin defined (meaning \- admin will control the arrangement of the team that the user sees once entering the page)
2. user will be able to sort the team manually
2.1 above the team photos and under the free text part will be a drop down, titled "סדר על פי"
2.2 by clicking on the top-down the user will be able to choose between t different categories \-
א'\-ת'
ת'\-א'
2.3 by clicking on the א'\-ת' option \- the team will be sorted in alphabetical order \- by first name
2.4 by clicking on the ת'\-א' option \- the team will be sorted in a reverse alphabetical order \- by first name
3. If the user chose to sort the chefs manually two things will change \- 

3.1 the drop-down title that was "סדר על פי" will change to the option he chose (meaning to "א'\-ת' *or* to "ת'\-את)

3.2 a third option will be added to the drop down "אפס"
4. by clicking on the "אפס" option the arrangement team will go back to the one admin has defined (meaning \- the "first view" option

4.1 id the user chose the "אפס" option, the drop down title will change back to "סדר על פי"
